{"word":"Baal","slug":"baal","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Baal</b> <a href=\"#/H1168\">H1168</a><br/><a href=\"#/G896\">G896</a> <br/> 1. An idol of the Phenicians, god of the sun<br/> - Wickedly worshiped by the Israelites in the time of the judges<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=2&verse=23'>Jdg 2:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=4'>1Sa 7:4</a> <br/> - Wickedly worshiped by the kingdom of Israel:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=16'>2Ki 17:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=23&verse=13'>Jer 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1'>Hos 1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=13&verse=1'>Hos 13:1</a><br/> b Under Ahab<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=33'>1Ki 16:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=18'>1Ki 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=18'>1Ki 19:18</a><br/> b Under Jehoram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=2'>2Ki 3:2</a><br/> b by the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=21&verse=3'>2Ki 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=22&verse=4'>2Ch 22:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=24&verse=7'>2Ch 24:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=2'>2Ch 28:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=33&verse=3'>2Ch 33:3</a><br/> - Jeremiah expostulates against the worship of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=8'>Jer 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=23'>Jer 2:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=9'>Jer 7:9</a> <br/> - Alters of, destroyed:<br/> b by Gideon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=32'>Jdg 6:32</a><br/> b by Jehoiada<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=11&verse=18'>2Ki 11:18</a><br/> b by Josiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=5'>2Ki 23:5</a><br/> - Prophets of, slain by Elijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=40'>1Ki 18:40</a> <br/> - All worshipers of, destroyed by Jehu<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=25'>2Ki 10:25</a> <br/> 2. A Benjamite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=8&verse=30'>1Ch 8:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=36'>1Ch 9:36</a><br/> 3. A Reubenite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=5'>1Ch 5:5</a><br/> 4. A city in the tribe of Simeon<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=33'>1Ch 4:33</a> <br/> - Called Baalath-Beer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=8'>Jos 19:8</a> "}]}